# docs/evidence/<descriptive-name>/ can still be committed.
docs/evidence/*-2026-*/
docs/evidence/all-features-*/
docs/evidence/preview-all-3-*/
docs/evidence/one-surface-*/
docs/evidence/dashboard-*/
docs/evidence/genie-*/
docs/evidence/powerbi-*/
